      <p style="font-family:var(--font); font-size:18px; color:#fff; line-height:1.7; max-width:560px; margin:0 auto;">Faith is not passive. It acts. Discipline is not punishment. It is the architecture of the person you are becoming. Performance is not a gift. It is built. One locked-in habit at a time.</p>
